name: Tab Age Tracker v1.7
body:
Tab Age Tracker v1.7 is a stable release with the following key features and improvements:

- Fixed tab sorting functionality, particularly for 'newest to oldest' sorting
- Improved handling of unknown age tabs
- Enhanced filter UI for better usability
- Added 'What's New' section highlighting feature improvements
- Fixed date extraction for special URL patterns
- Improved UI responsiveness and tooltip explanations
